    "text": "Dee? Where are you? I've seen her!",
    "from": "0:02",
    "to": "0:04",
    "cn": "迪伊？你在哪儿？我看见她了！"
  },
  {
    "text": "Over there!",
    "from": "0:04",
    "to": "0:06",
    "cn": "在那边！"
  },
  {
